========
1. Grab an attractive serving plate ; flat glass or black works nicely.
2. Slice the tomatoes thinly and scatter onto plate.
3. Sprinkle with salt , then scatter all over the basil leaves.
4. Drizzle over the vinegar and oil.
5. Cover with cling film and leave at room temperature until ready to serve.
